A ``setproctitle`` implementation for Python
============================================

The library allows a process to change its title (as display by system tools
such as ``ps`` and ``top``).

The procedure is hardly portable between different system.
A `good implementation`_ is provided by PostgreSQL_. 


.. good implementation: http://doxygen.postgresql.org/ps__status_8c-source.html
.. PostgreSQL: http://www.postgresql.org




